---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About - Dileepa Bandara"
  description="Learn more about Dileepa Bandara, a software engineer passionate about AI, cloud computing, and software development."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-8">About Me</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        Hi, I'm Dileepa Bandara, a passionate software engineer with expertise
        in Artificial Intelligence, Cloud Computing, and modern software
        development practices.
      </p>

      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        I love exploring cutting-edge technologies and sharing my knowledge
        through this blog. Whether it's building AI-powered applications,
        architecting scalable cloud solutions, or diving deep into software
        engineering best practices, I'm always excited to learn and teach.
      </p>

      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        When I'm not coding, you can find me contributing to open-source
        projects, attending tech conferences, or experimenting with new tools
        and frameworks.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-light p-6 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">What I Write About</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
        <li>• Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</li>
        <li>• Cloud Computing (Azure, AWS, GCP)</li>
        <li>• Software Architecture and Design Patterns</li>
        <li>• DevOps and Infrastructure as Code</li>
        <li>• Modern Web Development</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
